44
00:03:48,210 --> 00:03:54,380
It could mean scoping something else or increasing
the cost or even increasing the time to fit

45
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:55,540
it in.

46
00:03:55,540 --> 00:04:01,210
The important part is that it's managed and
leveraged for value, not feared.

